title: Andy Warstar - 06-18-07 Melbourne, Oz
description:
Here&#039;s Andy Warstar playing in a restaurant in Melbourne, Australia called "Lentil

As Anything", a "pay as you feel" restaurant. They fed Andy, who played in a

cramped corner by the door (where the drunk chick, who is on the recording, kept

accidentally bashing Andy on the ass even while he played, not even missing a

beat to the surprise and adulation of the audience!)


A fun, noisy restaurant performance... it&#039;s just like being there when you can&#039;t

afford to eat out - something a lot of punk rockers can probably relate to. And

if you live in Melbourne, please get a copy of this show to the kids that run

that restaurant. They are awesome and rad and stuff. Peace.
